(AI Quant Investment Engine) Tj
T*
(Silver Layer Metrics - Beginner Friendly Finance Guide) Tj
T*
(Generated on: 2026-02-26 19:57:11) Tj
T*
T*
(WHO THIS IS FOR) Tj
T*
(This document is for non-finance users, junior developers, analysts, and stakeholders.) Tj
T*
(It explains what each silver layer metric means, how we calculate it in code,) Tj
T*
(and how to interpret it in simple language.) Tj
T*
T*
(IMPORTANT CONTEXT) Tj
T*
(In this project, silver metrics are generated in src/etl/pyspark_etl.py.) Tj
T*
(They are used by the ML model to produce confidence scores and investment signals.) Tj
T*
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(1\) QUICK IDEA: WHY WE USE THESE METRICS) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(Raw price alone is noisy. A single close value does not tell the full story.) Tj
T*
(These metrics answer 3 practical questions:) Tj
T*
(- Trend: Is price generally moving up, down, or sideways?) Tj
T*
(- Momentum: Is movement getting stronger or weaker?) Tj
T*
(- Risk/Volatility: How unstable is the movement?) Tj
T*
T*
(The model gets a better signal when all three are provided together.) Tj
T*
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(2\) THE SILVER LAYER INPUTS) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(For each asset symbol and each date, we start with OHLCV:) Tj
T*
(- Open) Tj
T*
(- High) Tj
T*
(- Low) Tj
T*
(- Close) Tj
T*
(- Volume) Tj
T*
T*
(Most formulas in silver layer use Close, High, and Low.) Tj
T*
T*
(Notation used below:) Tj
T*
(- C_t = Close on day t) Tj
T*
(- H_t = High on day t) Tj
T*
(- L_t = Low on day t) Tj
T*
(- PrevClose_t = C_\(t-1\)) Tj
T*
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(3\) WORKED EXAMPLE DATA \(SIMPLE\)) Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(Assume one symbol has these 7 close prices:) Tj
T*
(Day1=100, Day2=102, Day3=101, Day4=104, Day5=106, Day6=105, Day7=107) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
